										<div style="float: left;"><strong class="xar-sub">Subject: Just wondering what other parents are doing this summer
</strong></div>
					<div style="clear: both;"></div>
				</div>
				<div>
															<p>to support learning for your child with a learning disability.  </p>
<p>My name is Gina.  I have an 8 yr old dd who has struggled in reading since day one.  Her dad has dyslexia.  We are having her tested for it this fall.  We were really hoping to get her into the clinic this summer but that is as early as they can see her.  We do a lot of work during the summer to try to catch her up.  </p>
<p>Just wondering what other parents are doing.<br />
Gina</p>
									</div>
							</td>
